            "content": [
              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "Here are some of the **latest major headlines today (Friday, 26 June 2026)**, based on current headline feeds:\n\n### UK (top developing stories)\n- **June heat records broken again** in the UK, with **temperatures still rising**. ([news.sky.com](https://news.sky.com/uk))  \n- **Severe thunderstorms disrupting airports**, with warnings of **knock-on impacts**. ([news.sky.com](https://news.sky.com/uk))  \n- **Sheffield tram network suspended due to extreme heat**. ([news.sky.com](https://news.sky.com/uk))  \n- Reported: **Teenage boy dies after entering a lake during the heatwave**. ([news.sky.com](https://news.sky.com/uk))  \n\n### World / geopolitics\n- **Putin and Lukashenko hold talks** at a tense point in the **Ukraine war**. ([news.google.com](https://news.google.com/topics/CAAqIQgKIhtDQkFTRGdvSUwyMHZNSEJ6TlRNU0FuSjFLQUFQAQ?ceid=US%3Aen&hl=en-US))  \n- **Strait of Hormuz**: reports of a **ship attack** and continued high tension around traffic through the strait. ([news.google.com](https://news.google.com/topics/CAAqJggKIiBDQkFTRWdvSUwyMHZNRFZxYUdjU0FtVnVHZ0pWVXlnQVAB))  \n\n### US (politics/economy)\n- **US Supreme Court**: AP reports the court **cleared the way** for the Trump administration to potentially revive a **restrictive asylum policy**. ([news.google.com](https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMITuzgEw4fQo?ceid=US%3Aen&hl=en-US))  \n- AP also highlights: **a key inflation gauge rose to a 3-year high (May)**, pointing to ongoing affordability pressure. ([news.google.com](https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMITuzgEw4fQo?ceid=US%3Aen&hl=en-US))  \n\nIf you tell me what you want (UK-only, world-only, business/markets, tech, sport), I can narrow this to the most relevant 10–15 headlines.",
